# Docker build context exclusions.
#
# The Dockerfile only COPYs `scripts/*` and `.heartlib/`. Everything else
# in this directory is either runtime state (mounts), unrelated tooling,
# or huge model/output artifacts that would balloon the build context to
# hundreds of GB.
#
# Symptoms this fixes:
#   - `docker compose build slopfinity` failing with
#     "no permission to read from comfy-outputs/experiments/config.json"
#     (root-owned because written from inside a previous container run).
#   - Build context transfer taking minutes/hours and using GB of RAM.

# Model / output / cache trees (the worst offenders).
# comfy-models is a symlink to /mnt/downloads — never include.
comfy-models
comfy-models/**
comfy-outputs
comfy-outputs/**
comfy-input
comfy-input/**
huggingface-cache
huggingface-cache/**
ComfyUI_output
ComfyUI_output/**
ComfyUI-LTXVideo
ComfyUI-LTXVideo/**
LTX-2
LTX-2/**
outputs
outputs/**
qwen-outputs
qwen-outputs/**

# JS / Python build artifacts.
node_modules
node_modules/**
__pycache__
__pycache__/**
.pytest_cache
.pytest_cache/**
.venv
.venv/**
venv
venv/**
*.pyc

# Test / dev artifacts.
test-results
test-results/**
playwright-report
playwright-report/**
e2e/artifacts
e2e/artifacts/**
js-tests
js-tests/**
logs
logs/**
demo
demo/**
ui-rebuild
ui-rebuild/**

# Git internals and editor metadata.
.git
.git/**
.github
.github/**
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.claude
.claude/**
.gemini
.gemini/**
.letta
.letta/**
.kilo
.kilo/**
.pytest_cache

# Top-level scratch files the build doesn't need.
generated_music.wav
generate_music.py
debug_uvicorn.py
test_video.py
concat.txt
-.o
*.log
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-*
*.db
*.db-*

# Slopfinity application code — mounted as a volume at runtime, not
# baked into the image. Keep it out of context.
slopfinity
slopfinity/**

# Pipelines / docs / branding — also volume-mounted or not used at build.
pipelines
pipelines/**
docs
docs/**
branding
branding/**

# Bin (precompiled artifacts, not needed for build).
bin
bin/**

# Dotfiles that occasionally contain secrets.
.env
.env.*
*.env

# Editor swap files.
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
